dataset_id: BOREAS TE-18 Landsat TM Maximum Likelihood Classification Image of the NSA
title: BOREAS TE-18 Landsat TM Maximum Likelihood Classification Image of the NSA
summary: The objective of this classification is to provide the BOREAS investigators with a data product that characterizes the land cover of the NSA. A Landsat-5 TM image from 20-Aug-1988 was used to derive this classification.  A standard supervised maximum likelihood classification approach was used to produce this classification.
